{"tid":2003623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普讚揚本地生產口罩高質　不似「其他國家」的劣質口罩","createTime":"2020-05-06T02:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T14:40:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7d61e5c4ad0cf7e9c65e7e6e81ec479012205710","tid":2003623,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"一直拒絕戴口罩的美國總統特朗普，在亞利桑那州視察一間口罩生產工廠後表示，口罩廠將會每月生產2千萬個N95口罩，是奇蹟一樣的成就，不單救美國人一命，未來亦可協助其他國家建立防護物資儲備，令美國人感到自豪。他又讚揚廠房生產的N95口罩質素很好，不像其他國家對外運送的劣質口罩。特朗普在視察期間，戴上護目鏡，但他與隨行官員都無戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又指，口罩廠在短短5星期內落成，為當地創造500個就業職位，認為政府多年來都將工業生產活動外判其他國家，是時候奪回製造業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285437&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1285437%26csid%3D261_341&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=11b72650\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1285437&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"af1deab4072020204c3fc3fa72d95068299b440d","tid":2003623,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"話時話美國防貪污制度係點？<br />\n高質=防貪、監管做得好"},{"pid":"75be050594d69f1b804211f0a4f3d9cf13c61489","tid":2003623,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2b2ebb16a7cc9abe941b13b248008edabcceec","tid":2003623,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af1deab4072020204c3fc3fa72d95068299b440d","tid":2003623,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"話時話美國防貪污制度係點？<br />\n高質=防貪、監管做得好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"made in USA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass